symc.name: STD_INPUT_HANDLE
symc.desc: The standard input device. Initially, this is the console input buffer, CONIN$

symc.name: STD_OUTPUT_HANDLE
symc.desc: The standard output device. Initially, this is the active console screen buffer, CONOUT$.

symc.name: STD_ERROR_HANDLE
symc.desc: The standard error device. Initially, this is the active console screen buffer, CONOUT$.
